{"tid":788060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬哈蒂爾：暫時取消中國項目 不希望馬來西亞破產","createTime":"2018-08-21T07:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T09:29:56.000Z","uid":14918,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3d02aca9b844d2aa389ab81c9e9ed81ad10d461d","tid":788060,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:37:54.000Z","msg":"　　《經濟通通訊社２１日專訊》外電報道，馬來西亞總理馬哈蒂爾在華訪問期間表示，中國資<br />\n助的２００億美元東部沿海鐵路（ＥＣＲＬ）及沙巴天然氣管道項目將暫時取消。<br />\n　　馬哈蒂爾在北京對媒體發表談話時表示，上述這些項目將取消，直到馬來西亞能負擔得起的<br />\n時候，相信中國本身也不希望看到馬來西亞變成一個破產的國家。<br />\n　　馬來西亞總理辦公室證實了馬哈蒂爾在北京對記者的評論。（ｂｉ）"},{"pid":"e9dde47cca94163c8833382d845dcebbe4b26508","tid":788060,"uid":64191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:39:00.000Z","msg":"日日贏"},{"pid":"f6fe3479fe31985b0e093f49641c55e653a7617f","tid":788060,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:39:57.000Z","msg":"排華開始,講到出哂面...."},{"pid":"e5a535b131f83f4fb2344c922608eab367c9d78b","tid":788060,"uid":19287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:41:52.000Z","msg":"比返個落台梯大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e1bcdbd203dddf7f6ec8a0f1875287d2a3259e","tid":788060,"uid":43009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:54:17.000Z","msg":"照投資 不過用榴槤找數得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n破產就用榴槤還債"},{"pid":"dbad73ecf326c30a3e2901fd8caaa6c26df73c5b","tid":788060,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T09:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}